Credit~
A new save: Lily level 1
Race: Temptress.
To create this character I used the following ways:
HQ Hair 1Fine by Yuril: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/7627
2Hair Pack by newermind43: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/3809
3Calientes Female Body Mod Big Bottom Edition-CBBE-by Caliente: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2666
4Bright Eyes v1-3 by Skree000: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2464 #
5Enhanced Character Edit by tktk: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/12951
6Temptress Race by Psychos1s and Brokefoot:http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/18717/?tab=3&navtag=%2Fajax%2Fmodimages%2F%3Fuser%3D0%26id%3D18717
7Hair packs of Fallout3 by Radioragae:http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/17993
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
~Bugs~
To equip the character with the helmet, the hair disappears, this bug belongs Temptress Race mode. Maybe in the future we will create a fix to everyone's satisfaction.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
~Installation~
Extract and copy the saves folder\ my Games.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
~OBS~
Comments about this way are welcome, provided they observe a civilized language. So, if you do not download, do not bother commenting wrong. Thx!
